abstract: "ZeroGateSim is speculative research software for testing a zero-gate dimensional-emergence grammar in generated toy fields. The v1.0-alpha proof-of-concept tested a final trinary earned-one witness across adversarial distinction, polarity, and relation corpora."
keywords:
  - zero-gate
  - trinary logic
  - earned-one
  - toy simulation
  - dimensional emergence
  - proof-of-concept
